{"tid":614120,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"好友:干地迫切想離開車路士 他不接受沒有話語權","createTime":"2018-04-02T08:51:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-03T05:40:46.000Z","uid":147522,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"392cd21d6d1e11389e2578cf30aed73500452689","tid":614120,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T08:51:57.000Z","msg":"作客意大利天空體育擔任球評時，曾是干地隊友的維亞利表示，干地目前十分急迫地想要離隊，他不能接受球會的轉會事務自己不能過問。<br />\n　　「干地已經迫不及待想要離開車路士了。」維亞利表示，「他無法忍受球會不論買人還是賣人都無視自己的意見。事實就是，車路士更想要的只是一名對球會高層言聽計從的教練。」<br />\n　　「重返意大利國家隊也好，執教PSG也好，干地一定能再次找到一個讓自己贏得冠軍的地方。有的是合同等著他簽字。」<br />\n　　在1992至1996年間，維亞利和干地曾在祖雲達斯當過4個賽季的隊友，兩人曾一同跟隨祖記奪得1次歐冠盃冠軍，1次意甲冠軍和1次意大利盃冠軍。"},{"pid":"447005471c3e30b27a1ca1d1270afb94fc9bf48a","tid":614120,"uid":10176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T10:45:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b1b76d7e996cee50e8fcc3ccc3d9e3083e02f09","tid":614120,"uid":30768,"like":4,"dislike":5,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T10:47:48.000Z","msg":"廢就廢啦，帶轟帶到做阿仙奴私家雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"757d44b1e21ac0b1d3eef279e42d6aa9ee30ad79","tid":614120,"uid":7190,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"447005471c3e30b27a1ca1d1270afb94fc9bf48a","tid":614120,"uid":10176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T10:45:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T12:27:55.000Z","msg":"dllm"},{"pid":"2d6c3e913c1867929c2a04ef90975ec2146e1b0d","tid":614120,"uid":32722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T12:30:41.000Z","msg":"頭四不保就話決定走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31ae552c2b347def6ba0438745dbb8aa87ad1e84","tid":614120,"uid":33660,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T12:3